<h1>🏆 You won <%= @payout %>!</h1>

<p>Hi <%= @user.display_name %>,</p>

<p>
  Congratulations — your entry finished
  <strong>#<%= @rank %></strong> in <strong><%= @contest.name %></strong>
  and won <strong><%= @payout %></strong>.
</p>

<p>Your winnings have settled on-chain. Head back to the contest to see the final leaderboard:</p>

<p><%= link_to "View the contest →".html_safe, @contest_url %></p>

<p>If the button doesn't work, copy and paste this URL into your browser:</p>
<p><%= @contest_url %></p>

<p>Thanks for playing.</p>

<p>— Turf Monster</p>
